body_html:
@arundasan91
I'm sorry for my wrong information,
I didn't test the examples well.

Now I test ios_examples/camera,
I can build it without any modification for bulid settings or Info.plist (but set Team to run on real device).
But when I try to run the app, it crashes as you said.

I can run ios_example/simple though,
I think the error is not related to Tensorflow library,
and need modification for application code.

It is better to ask in other place about the crash (StackOverflow),
and send a pull request to fix the issue :)

@arundasan91 
I'm sorry for my wrong information,
I didn't test the examples well.

Now I test ios_examples/camera,
I can build it without any modification for bulid settings or `Info.plist` (but set `Team` to run on real device).
But when I try to run the app, it crashes as you said.

I can run ios_example/simple though,
I think the error is not related to Tensorflow library,
and need modification for application code.

It is better to ask in other place about the crash (StackOverflow),
and send a pull request to fix the issue :)
